Input file

lines.txt
------------

Specifies the content of your table.

each line has
row col followed by characters to go into that entry in the table

row is an integer  0, 1...
col is a character m, n...  

The number of characters per entry is always the same (i.e. VM).  

Run mat.out to see what your output should look like.

Feel free to change lines.txt to try different R, C and VM in mat.cpp


